@startuml
!theme mono

title PAY 서비스 - 구독 구매

participant "PayController" as ctrl
participant "SubscriptionService" as svc
participant "SubscriptionRepository" as repo
participant "AuthService(E)" as auth
participant "Apple IAP / Google Play(E)" as iap
database "PostgreSQL(E)" as db
database "Redis Cache(E)" as cache

-> ctrl : POST /api/v1/subscriptions/purchase\n{plan_id, receipt, provider}
activate ctrl

ctrl -> ctrl : 요청 검증 (plan_id 유효성, receipt 존재)

ctrl -> svc : purchaseSubscription(user_id, plan_id, receipt, provider)
activate svc

== 영수증 서버 측 검증 (Circuit Breaker + Retry) ==
svc -> iap : 영수증 서버 검증 요청
activate iap

alt 영수증 검증 성공
    iap --> svc : 검증 완료 (transaction_id, product_id)
    deactivate iap

    == 구독 상태 저장 ==
    svc -> repo : 구독 정보 저장/갱신
    activate repo
    repo -> db : subscriptions 저장\n(user_id, plan=Trip Pass/Pro,\nstatus=ACTIVE, start_at, expires_at)
    db --> repo : subscription_id
    deactivate repo

    svc -> repo : 결제 이력 저장
    activate repo
    repo -> db : payment_records 삽입\n(transaction_id, amount, provider)
    db --> repo : 저장 완료
    deactivate repo

    == JWT 클레임 갱신 (구독 티어 즉시 반영) ==
    svc -> auth : 구독 티어 변경 요청 (user_id, new_tier)
    activate auth
    auth -> cache : 기존 세션 토큰 즉시 무효화
    activate cache
    cache --> auth : 무효화 완료
    deactivate cache
    auth --> svc : 새 Access Token 발급 완료
    deactivate auth

    svc --> ctrl : 201 Created\n{subscription_id, tier, new_access_token, activated_features}

else 영수증 검증 실패
    iap --> svc : 검증 실패
    deactivate iap
    svc --> ctrl : 402 Payment Required\n{error: "결제 검증 실패"}

else 결제 Gateway 장애 (Circuit Breaker OPEN)
    svc --> ctrl : 503 Service Unavailable
end

deactivate svc

ctrl --> : 201 Created\n{구독 정보 + 새 토큰}
deactivate ctrl

@enduml
